{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ART IS RIFLE is an open-world, FPS puzzle game with rhythmic bullets and psychedelic art styles. Powered by Unreal Engine 5 and much passion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PSYCHEDELIC REINVENTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a psychedelic adventure through first-of-its-kind mind altering core gameplay mechanics, beyond visual and auditory designs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486730/extras/Bullets_Painting_Intro,short,600p,35.gif?t=1734271189\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a world of puzzles where tutorials are optional, and discovery is key! Puzzles are your canvas, solve them your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A work of art is a puzzle; when solved, it exposes the hidden layers of meaning and symbolism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MUSIC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The whole world is your drum kit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VISUALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a visually striking game that dances with a fusion of intense colors and mind-altering, psychedelic elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486730/extras/PPM_Transition_1.0sec_Final_GIF,short,600p,30.gif?t=1734271189\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"That Was Easy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486730/4a295d149f3ecaa589e762da7881b2b417b73bd8.jpg"},{"name":"Was that A Boss Fight?!","path":